&lt;p&gt;Service cover 07:30 - 20:00 Monday to Friday / Depending on experience weekend working and Bank holidays are an expected part of the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 7 Trainee Advanced Clinical Practitioner or a Band 8a Qualified Advanced Clinical Practitioner to join our existing team within Care of the Elderly. The post holder will be part of an established team working within Care of the Elderly at UHCW and Rugby St Cross Hospital. Successful applicants will be required to rotate between both sites if service needs require.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exciting developments within the specialty include the provision of an ANP led bed base and the development of frailty services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A trainee post will be paid at band 7 until completion of MSc programme and all competences deemed necessary for autonomous practice.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
